<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
	<meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
	</head>

	<body>
		<h1>Congratulations!</h1>
		<hr>
		<p>You have received a booking from <strong><%=@customer.first_name%> <%=@customer.last_name%></strong></p>

		<p>
			<h3>Your listing: <%=@listing.name%></h3>
			<strong>Check in:</strong> <%=@booking.check_in%><br>
			<strong>Check out:</strong> <%=@booking.check_out%><br>
			<strong>Guests:</strong> <%=@booking.guests%><br>
			<strong>Price: </strong> <%=@listing.price%>
		</p>	
		<p>
			You can see details of your reservation with a click of the button below:
      <table class="btn-primary" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
        <tr>
          <td>
          	<%= link_to "Manage your booking", user_url(@listing.user_id) %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
		</p>
		<p>
		If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us or the user directly on email <%=@customer.email%> or phone <%=@customer.phone%>. 
		</p>
		<p>
		Thank you
		</p>
		Petr Duda<br>
		AirBnB Team
	</body>
</html>